title: Summary - Hurricane Tammy (AT5/AL202023)
author: nhcwebmaster@noaa.gov (NHC Webmaster)
summary:
...TAMMY MOVING NORTHEASTWARD OVER THE SOUTHWESTERN ATLANTIC...
 As of 5:00 PM AST Tue Oct 24
 the center of Tammy was located near 24.6, -61.7
 with movement NE at 8 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 987 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 75 mph.
